ion of antigens in tissues could demonstrate viral DENV-2 replication and may correspond to natural infection in bats. Additional studies are needed to elucidate the exact role of these species in dengue epidemics.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Calder\u00f3n, Alfonso", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guzm\u00e1n, Camilo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Oviedo-Socarras, Teresa", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Mattar, Salim", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rodr\u00edguez, Virginia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Casta\u00f1eda, V\u00edctor", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Moraes Figueiredo, Luiz Tadeu", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5cbed9eecc0fb8f25f7208ca918e81ae", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/9f6dbac30b42a6efdf182de950c82b72e60a395f5f88462c77fb316198950770", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/YLSAYDD7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/YLSAYDD7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/641c0fe4fcab598391adbaed68906571!/b8992-11670", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "35", "title": "Tropical Medicine and Infectious Disease", "volume": "6"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/